{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"seed","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/seed","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p><code>seed</code>属性代表了<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTurbulence\"><code>&lt;feTurbulence&gt;</code></a>元素生成的伪随机数的开始数字。</p>\n\n<p>如果没有指定这个属性，它等效于指定了一个<code>0</code>值。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td><em>None</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\" title=\"/en-US/docs/SVG/Content_type#Number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/filters.html#feTurbulenceSeedAttribute\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用<code>seed</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTurbulence\"><code>&lt;feTurbulence&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"seed","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"seed","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/seed","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/seed/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.c